<article id="post-21514" class="post-21514 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-critical-thinking category-economics category-law category-the-war-years tag-articles-of-confederation tag-commissary-certificates tag-continental-currency tag-forfeiture-act tag-robert-morris">
	<div class="search-post-main">
